    "Both metrics are considered appropriate for the performance evaluation of topic models (Blei et al. 2003; Ogunleye et al. 2023).",
    "Lastly, we manually inspect the terms across the topics to ensure adequate human interpretation.",
    "This section presents our two-fold results.",
    "The first part presents the bibliometric analysis results, and the second part presents the results from the TM analysis.",
    "Thus, this paper discusses and synthesises results from both approaches to proffer insights and recommendations."
